name: Holiday wishes from the Hubble Space Telescope
description:
In the new Hubble image of the galaxy M74 we can also see a smattering of bright pink regions decorating the spiral arms.

Name:	M74, Phantom Galaxy
Type:	Local Universe : Galaxy : Type : Spiral

3,629 editions for the known 3,629 planetary systems to date.
